      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="apply-missing-submission-policy" data-step-uuid="1b83bbe0-3e18-4d42-8807-efd6260fc3c1">
    <h2 id="apply-missing-submission-policy" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Apply Missing Submission Policy</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/908/270/original/e2ec4caa-f12a-4bce-b641-efd10685392b.png" srcset="" alt="Apply Missing Submission Policy" height="272" width="424">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_96b392d5-d49e-4ada-9387-7bfcf9e5fd9a" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Automatically apply grade for missing submissions</strong> checkbox. Selecting this checkbox will automatically apply the grade you set for any missing submissions in the course. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

