        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view-grade-detail-tray" data-step-uuid="571ffac1-4539-4fb3-a9d0-474d85659f4d">
    <h3 id="view-grade-detail-tray" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Grade Detail Tray</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/245/884/original/a289fa2d-2883-4d4b-9a3f-3324d4a049c6.png" srcset="" alt="View Grade Detail Tray" height="611" width="323">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_9e61c404-cdc5-48bf-a6cd-c2eec12cc69e" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Grade Detail Tray, you can view details about the submission. When a submission applies to a missing policy, the Grade Detail Tray displays the given grade. To remove the late penalty from a submission, enter a grade in the grade field. Once a grade has been manually assigned, the Missing submission policy no longer applies and the label is automatically removed.</p>
  </div>
